name: Zombie Jack Daniels shirt
description: yep we know, several bands have done this before, but we just had to do one to acknowledge the bands favorite cocktail. Also we think we did a better job by mimicking the whiskey's label and infusing our own touch of death grind and horror. 100% cotton.

name: Zombie Koozie
description: It's that time of year again where you'll be in the back yard, blasting some zombie hate brigade, a cooler full of brews and you'll look at that beer bottle and think to yourself, "damn, this thing is naked". By that time your hand has already warmed up the bottle and your cursing because you didn't grab that zombie hate brigade koozie at the last show... Well, here they are, just for the picking and the summertime grind! Awesome full color design on both sides of the koozie (art by the popular NEV), durable double stiching on both sides, and folds up nicely to fit in your pocket when you've had your last drink. (beer in picture does not come with koozie).

name: Fistful of entrails
description: *NEW* Fistful of entrails shirt. Wicked zombie art on the front by NEV (singer for the band Loathsome). And zombie hand on the back holding eyeballs and entrails.

name: zombie hate brigade CD's
description:
ZOMBIE HATE BRIGADE's CD's. Now we have an easy way for each person to order each CD. Just CLICK below and select the CD you want to order. Each drop down is a different CD title. 

Every order placed will also receive the zombie hate brigade Embroidered patch and sticker combo pack for FREE!

 The fist album (self titled) and the 2nd EP (hideous beyond belief) are SOLD OUT, please do not ask for these releases.

(The LP version is the one issued by the band on their indy label GETUPANDKILL MUSIC, not the crash music inc re-release. Only a few left.)
